Maintainer: ichthyosaurus
Summary: Change the remorse timer 'X' icon to a check mark
Description:
- This patch keeps the current remorse timer design but changes the 'X' icon to a check mark.
-
- Another patch is available [here](https://openrepos.net/content/ichthyosaurus/patch-remove-icon-remorse-timer)
- that removes the icon completely.

DiscussionLink: https://openrepos.net/content/ichthyosaurus/patch-check-mark-remorse-timer
